                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-409-18421212 t18421212-409-punishment-114"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO MONDAY, JANUARY 2ND</hi>, 1843.</p>
